collectionMetadata.name: Volunteers With The Rehabilitation And Protection Group (RPG) Of MSF
collectionMetadata.description: Volunteers with the Rehabilitation and Protection Group (RPG) of MSF work closely with MSF to provide support to children, young persons and families who require rehabilitation and protection. Volunteers are important and they act as befrienders and mentors, giving guidance and support to their charges.
collectionMetadata.managedBy: Ministry of Social and Family Development
